rows.label: tev999925_SEL0031
rows.name: This BLADE operative is standing by for orders.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999925_MSG0101
rows.name: Good day. You look as well as ever.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999925_MSG2001
rows.name: Understood. I'll submit a request for division support.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999925_MSG2101
rows.name:
Fight with confidence knowing that my division will
have your back.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999925_MSG3001
rows.name:
If you think I could be of help to you,
I'd be happy to try.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999925_MSG3101
rows.name: Working with you makes my heart sing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999925_MSG5001
rows.name: I'm occupied at the moment. Perhaps we can talk later?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999925_MSG5101
rows.name:
I'm sorry, but I can't pull myself away from this.
Could you inquire again later?[ST:wait ]
